<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <title>About Us - Ecommerce</title>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #f8f9fa; }
        .about-container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 2rem auto; background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .mission { background: #e9ecef; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .benefits { margin-top: 2rem; }
        .benefit-item { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .benefit-item h5 { color: #28a745; }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body class="page-shell">
    <%- include('partials/topbar') %>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-container">
            <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Ecomme</h1>

            <div class="mission">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="lead">To revolutionize e-commerce by leveraging blockchain technology to create a transparent, secure, and rewarding shopping experience for our customers.</p>
            </div>

            <h3>Why Blockchain?</h3>
            <p>Blockchain technology provides the foundation for trustless transactions, where buyers and sellers can interact without needing intermediaries. By using smart contracts, we ensure that all transactions are transparent, immutable, and automatically executed according to predefined rules.</p>

            <div class="benefits">
                <h3>Key Benefits</h3>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="benefit-item">
                            <h5>Trustless Transactions</h5>
                            <p>Smart contracts eliminate the need for intermediaries, ensuring that payments are only released when conditions are met, protecting both buyers and sellers.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="benefit-item">
                            <h5>Transparency in Order Status</h5>
                            <p>Every step of the order process is recorded on the blockchain, providing complete visibility into order status, delivery tracking, and payment confirmations.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="benefit-item">
                            <h5>Automated Loyalty Rewards</h5>
                            <p>Loyalty tokens are automatically awarded through smart contracts upon successful delivery confirmation, creating a seamless reward system.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="benefit-item">
                            <h5>Improved Customer Retention</h5>
                            <p>By providing transparent processes and rewarding customer loyalty, we build long-term relationships and encourage repeat business.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p class="mt-4">Our platform demonstrates how blockchain can transform traditional e-commerce, making it more secure, transparent, and customer-centric.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
